summary: Like how are you going to attack Sansa for not having any freedom by stating that Jon, Bran, Arya, Daenerys and Sam had some so...
body: Like how are you going to attack Sansa for not having any freedom by stating that Jon, Bran, Arya, Daenerys and Sam had some so it makes them superior? For starters, if Sansa hadn’t made the CHOICE to fight to get her home back even though everyone else gave up on Winterfell…Jon, Bran, Arya, Daenerys and Sam wouldn’t be able to go there and they’ll all be split apart, and no one would have managed to overcome the white walkers and at the end, everyone would die.
